---
---

<div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-label reveal">The journey so far</div>
    <h2 class="section-heading reveal reveal-delay-1">
        10 years of <span class="highlight">building</span>.
    </h2>

    <div class="timeline">
        <div class="timeline-item reveal reveal-delay-1">
            <div class="timeline-date">2025 &mdash; present</div>
            <div class="timeline-role">Frontend Developer</div>
            <div class="timeline-company">Akka &middot; Gothenburg</div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item reveal reveal-delay-1">
            <div class="timeline-date">2025</div>
            <div class="timeline-role">Backend Developer (C#)</div>
            <div class="timeline-company">Hedin IT &middot; Gothenburg</div>
            <div class="timeline-note">TDD in 90% of the work. Bug-free deliveries.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item reveal reveal-delay-2">
            <div class="timeline-date">2023 &mdash; 2025</div>
            <div class="timeline-role">Software Developer &rarr; Tech Lead</div>
            <div class="timeline-company">Sembo Group &middot; Remote</div>
            <div class="timeline-note">31% of all commits in a team of 11. Headless CMS architecture.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item reveal reveal-delay-2">
            <div class="timeline-date">2022 &mdash; 2023</div>
            <div class="timeline-role">Head of Dev &rarr; CTO</div>
            <div class="timeline-company">NetConsult Sweden AB &middot; Gothenburg</div>
            <div class="timeline-note">Recruited 6 devs/designers in 6 months. Led 7 client products.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item reveal reveal-delay-3">
            <div class="timeline-date">2020 &mdash; 2022</div>
            <div class="timeline-role">Senior Engineer &rarr; Lead Developer</div>
            <div class="timeline-company">Telia Sverige &middot; Gothenburg</div>
            <div class="timeline-note">Knowledge sharing across 14 dev teams. Micro-frontend architecture for telia.se.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item reveal reveal-delay-3">
            <div class="timeline-date">2017 &mdash; 2020</div>
            <div class="timeline-role">Systems Developer</div>
            <div class="timeline-company">KITS AB &middot; Gothenburg</div>
            <div class="timeline-note">React, Angular, Vue &mdash; deep dive across multiple clients.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-item reveal reveal-delay-4">
            <div class="timeline-date">2011 &mdash; 2016</div>
            <div class="timeline-role">Service Coordinator &rarr; Team Lead &amp; Tools Dev</div>
            <div class="timeline-company">Hewlett Packard Enterprise &middot; Gothenburg</div>
            <div class="timeline-note">Built 8 internal tools. Led 10 support agents. Presidential nomination.</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .timeline {
        position: relative;
        padding-left: 32px;
    }

    .timeline::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        left: 7px;
        top: 0;
        bottom: 0;
        width: 2px;
        background: var(--border);
    }

    .timeline-item {
        position: relative;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        padding-left: 20px;
    }

    .timeline-item:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .section-heading {
        margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .timeline-item::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        left: -28px;
        top: 5px;
        width: 8px;
        height: 8px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: var(--purple);
        border: 3px solid var(--bg);
    }

    .timeline-item:first-child::before {
        box-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--purple);
    }

    .timeline-date {
        font-family: var(--mono);
        font-size: 12px;
        color: var(--purple);
        margin-bottom: 1px;
    }

    .timeline-role {
        font-size: 15px;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .timeline-company {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: var(--text-dim);
    }

    .timeline-note {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        margin-top: 1px;
        font-style: italic;
    }

    @media print {
        .timeline { padding-left: 24px; }
        .timeline-item { margin-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 14px; }
        .timeline-item::before { width: 8px; height: 8px; left: -22px; top: 5px; }
        .timeline-date { font-size: 8px; margin-bottom: 0; }
        .timeline-role { font-size: 10px; }
        .timeline-company { font-size: 8px; }
        .timeline-note { font-size: 8px; margin-top: 1px; }
    }
</style>
